com.epoch.assgts

Class AssgtQGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.assgts.AssgtQGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AssgtQGroupConstants, QuestionConstants, XMLConstants

    public class AssgtQGroup
extends Object
implements AssgtQGroupConstants, QuestionConstants
    Contains a question or a group of questions within an assignment, as well as their point value and, when there's just one question, which question must be answered correctly before this one can be displayed. When there is more than one question in this group, they are grouped into bundles of bundleSize consecutive questions; when an assignment is instantiated, ACE randomly chooses pick bundles for the student.
